    "title": "Career Opportunity Financial Analyst at Instamojo",
    "description": "We at Instamojo are looking for an experienced Financial Analyst based out of Jabalpur. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Instamojo:\nInstamojo is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Instamojo!",
